atering head.\", \"from\": 4128, \"to\": 4280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4148, \"end\": 4154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999999955801287, \"rank\": 3.924716711457781e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The average meal\", \"from\": 4128, \"to\": 4144}, {\"ngram\": \"about 2 kilograms\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4214}, {\"ngram\": \"4.4 pounds\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4226}, {\"ngram\": \"CO2\", \"from\": 4231, \"to\": 4234}, {\"ngram\": \"Philipp W\\u00fcrz\", \"from\": 4241, \"to\": 4253}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' catering head\", \"from\": 4255, \"to\": 4279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris aims to halve that by sourcing 80% of ingredients locally, cutting transport emissions, and offering spectators 60% plant-based foods.\", \"from\": 4281, \"to\": 4421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4281, \"end\": 4286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.239680119467233e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"80%\", \"from\": 4318, \"to\": 4321}, {\"ngram\": \"ingredients\", \"from\": 4325, \"to\": 4336}, {\"ngram\": \"transport emissions\", \"from\": 4354, \"to\": 4373}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 4388, \"to\": 4398}, {\"ngram\": \"60% plant-based foods\", \"from\": 4399, \"to\": 4420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Winning minds as well as tastebuds could take work.\", \"from\": 4423, \"to\": 4474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"minds\", \"from\": 4431, \"to\": 4436}, {\"ngram\": \"tastebuds\", \"from\": 4448, \"to\": 4457}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 4469, \"to\": 4473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Locally grown food, and supporting local farmers, are beautiful things,\\\" tennis playerVictoria Azarenkasaid.\", \"from\": 4475, \"to\": 4584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Locally grown food\", \"from\": 4476, \"to\": 4494}, {\"ngram\": \"local farmers\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4524}, {\"ngram\": \"beautiful things\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But \\\"when people are doing these big gestures, I am not fully convinced of the impact,\\\" she added of Paris' overall climate efforts.\", \"from\": 4585, \"to\": 4717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4686, \"end\": 4691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.239680119467233e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4595, \"to\": 4601}, {\"ngram\": \"these big gestures\", \"from\": 4612, \"to\": 4630}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another emissions-savings source is energy.\", \"from\": 4719, \"to\": 4762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another emissions-savings source\", \"from\": 4719, \"to\": 4751}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 4755, \"to\": 4761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Energy will represent only 1% of emissions, organizers said.\", \"from\": 4763, \"to\": 4823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Energy\", \"from\": 4763, \"to\": 4769}, {\"ngram\": \"only 1%\", \"from\": 4785, \"to\": 4792}, {\"ngram\": \"emissions\", \"from\": 4796, \"to\": 4805}, {\"ngram\": \"organizers\", \"from\": 4807, \"to\": 4817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They intend to use 100% renewable power from wind and solar farms, plus solar panels on some venues.\", \"from\": 4824, \"to\": 4924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"100% renewable power\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 4863}, {\"ngram\": \"wind\", \"from\": 4869, \"to\": 4873}, {\"ngram\": \"solar farms\", \"from\": 4878, \"to\": 4889}, {\"ngram\": \"solar panels\", \"from\": 4896, \"to\": 4908}, {\"ngram\": \"some venues\", \"from\": 4912, \"to\": 4923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stadiums and temporary venues will get power from the grid instead of diesel generators, which produce much CO2.\", \"from\": 4926, \"to\": 5038, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stadiums\", \"from\": 4926, \"to\": 4934}, {\"ngram\": \"temporary venues\", \"from\": 4939, \"to\": 4955}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 4965, \"to\": 4970}, {\"ngram\": \"the grid\", \"from\": 4976, \"to\": 4984}, {\"ngram\": \"diesel generators\", \"from\": 4996, \"to\": 5013}, {\"ngram\": \"much CO2\", \"from\": 5029, \"to\": 5037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Giant electrical plugs at venues will remain post-Games, removing the need for generators at future events.\", \"from\": 5039, \"to\": 5146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Giant electrical plugs\", \"from\": 5039, \"to\": 5061}, {\"ngram\": \"venues\", \"from\": 5065, \"to\": 5071}, {\"ngram\": \"post-Games\", \"from\": 5084, \"to\": 5094}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 5105, \"to\": 5113}, {\"ngram\": \"generators\", \"from\": 5118, \"to\": 5128}, {\"ngram\": \"future events\", \"from\": 5132, \"to\": 5145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reducing transportation-related emissions is arguably Paris' biggest challenge.\", \"from\": 5148, \"to\": 5227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5202, \"end\": 5207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.239680119467233e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"transportation-related emissions\", \"from\": 5157, \"to\": 5189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tourism officials expect 15.3 million visitors for the Olympics and Paralympics, including 1.9 million from outside France, with at least 850,000 taking long-haul flights.\", \"from\": 5228, \"to\": 5399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5344, \"end\": 5350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999999955801287, \"rank\": 3.924716711457781e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tourism officials\", \"from\": 5228, \"to\": 5245}, {\"ngram\": \"15.3 million visitors\", \"from\": 5253, \"to\": 5274}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5279, \"to\": 5291}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 5296, \"to\": 5307}, {\"ngram\": \"long-haul flights\", \"from\": 5381, \"to\": 5398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, there are low-carbon transport options - cycling routes, Metro trains, buses and other public transit - to all venues.\", \"from\": 5401, \"to\": 5529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5404, \"end\": 5409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.239680119467233e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"low-carbon transport options - cycling routes\", \"from\": 5421, \"to\": 5466}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 5468, \"to\": 5473}, {\"ngram\": \"all venues\", \"from\": 5518, \"to\": 5528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the inability to control how people get to the Olympics, or any big event, raises questions about whether humanity can afford such get-togethers at the cost of further climate damage.\", \"from\": 5531, \"to\": 5718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the inability\", \"from\": 5535, \"to\": 5548}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5564, \"to\": 5570}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5578, \"to\": 5590}, {\"ngram\": \"any big event\", \"from\": 5595, \"to\": 5608}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 5617, \"to\": 5626}, {\"ngram\": \"humanity\", \"from\": 5641, \"to\": 5649}, {\"ngram\": \"such get-togethers\", \"from\": 5661, \"to\": 5679}, {\"ngram\": \"the cost\", \"from\": 5683, \"to\": 5691}, {\"ngram\": \"further climate damage\", \"from\": 5695, \"to\": 5717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Maybe things like the Olympics have to be reconsidered,\\\" said Seth Warren Rose of the Eneref Institute, an advocacy and research group focused on sustainable development.\", \"from\": 5720, \"to\": 5891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5788, \"end\": 5794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warren_bioregion\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 4.099038201655785e-12, \"text\": \"Warren\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warren_bioregion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warren_bioregion\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 5727, \"to\": 5733}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5739, \"to\": 5751}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eneref Institute\", \"from\": 5803, \"to\": 5823}, {\"ngram\": \"an advocacy and research group\", \"from\": 5825, \"to\": 5855}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainable development\", \"from\": 5867, \"to\": 5890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having millions of people congregate in a single area is a very intensive thing.\\\"\", \"from\": 5892, \"to\": 5974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 5900, \"to\": 5908}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5912, \"to\": 5918}, {\"ngram\": \"a single area\", \"from\": 5933, \"to\": 5946}, {\"ngram\": \"a very intensive thing\", \"from\": 5950, \"to\": 5972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rose said organizers' efforts are laudable, but they should have gone further - reducing emissions beyond half and finding more ways to make sustainability a central fan experience.\", \"from\": 5976, \"to\": 6157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rose\", \"from\": 5976, \"to\": 5980}, {\"ngram\": \"organizers' efforts\", \"from\": 5986, \"to\": 6005}, {\"ngram\": \"further - reducing emissions\", \"from\": 6046, \"to\": 6074}, {\"ngram\": 