 to climate change, extremely harmful,\\\" Upright Project's Annu Nieminen said in a statement.\", \"from\": 6719, \"to\": 6995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the current sustainability discourse\", \"from\": 6730, \"to\": 6766}, {\"ngram\": \"companies' miniscule sustainability tweaks\", \"from\": 6799, \"to\": 6841}, {\"ngram\": \"greenwashing efforts\", \"from\": 6846, \"to\": 6866}, {\"ngram\": \"a difference\", \"from\": 6891, \"to\": 6903}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 6907, \"to\": 6921}, {\"ngram\": \"Upright Project's Annu Nieminen\", \"from\": 6943, \"to\": 6974}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 6983, \"to\": 6994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If the Paris 2024 sponsors are celebrated by the organizers for their 'sustainability,' that's contributing to the same harmful discourse.\\\"\", \"from\": 6996, \"to\": 7136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7004, \"end\": 7014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.252829539292627e-39, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the organizers\", \"from\": 7042, \"to\": 7056}, {\"ngram\": \"their 'sustainability\", \"from\": 7061, \"to\": 7082}, {\"ngram\": \"the same harmful discourse\", \"from\": 7108, \"to\": 7134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement, organizers said the Games presented \\\"a unique opportunity to encourage partner businesses to adopt more responsible practices.\\\"\", \"from\": 7138, \"to\": 7281, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 7141, \"to\": 7152}, {\"ngram\": \"organizers\", \"from\": 7154, \"to\": 7164}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 7170, \"to\": 7179}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique opportunity\", \"from\": 7191, \"to\": 7211}, {\"ngram\": \"partner businesses\", \"from\": 7225, \"to\": 7243}, {\"ngram\": \"more responsible practices\", \"from\": 7253, \"to\": 7279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For emissions it can not cut, Paris plans to compensate - a practice called offsetting.\", \"from\": 7283, \"to\": 7370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7313, \"end\": 7318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.239680119467233e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"emissions\", \"from\": 7287, \"to\": 7296}, {\"ngram\": \"a practice\", \"from\": 7341, \"to\": 7351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Planting trees, for example, could help take CO2 out of the atmosphere that the Games put in.\", \"from\": 7371, \"to\": 7464, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Planting trees\", \"from\": 7371, \"to\": 7385}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 7391, \"to\": 7398}, {\"ngram\": \"CO2\", \"from\": 7416, \"to\": 7419}, {\"ngram\": \"the atmosphere\", \"from\": 7427, \"to\": 7441}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 7447, \"to\": 7456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But offset markets are not well regulated, and investigations by news organizations have found some projects to be fraudulent while others miscalculated the quantity of emissions captured.\", \"from\": 7465, \"to\": 7653, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"offset markets\", \"from\": 7469, \"to\": 7483}, {\"ngram\": \"investigations\", \"from\": 7512, \"to\": 7526}, {\"ngram\": \"news organizations\", \"from\": 7530, \"to\": 7548}, {\"ngram\": \"some projects\", \"from\": 7560, \"to\": 7573}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 7597, \"to\": 7603}, {\"ngram\": \"the quantity\", \"from\": 7618, \"to\": 7630}, {\"ngram\": \"emissions\", \"from\": 7634, \"to\": 7643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organizers say they will continue to adapt sustainability plans as they go, including those in Tahiti.\", \"from\": 7655, \"to\": 7757, \"entities\"